ns0:Concept.displayName: Other ectopic pregnancy without intrauterine pregnancy
Other ectopic pregnancy with intrauterine pregnancy

ns0:DescribedValueSet.ns0:Purpose: (Clinical Focus: This value set contains concepts that represent diagnoses of cornual ectopic pregnancy.),(Data Element Scope: This value set may use Quality Data Model (QDM) category related to Diagnosis. The intent of this data element is to identify conditions that represent a cornual ectopic pregnancy.),(Inclusion Criteria: Includes only relevant concepts associated with codes representing a cornual ectopic pregnancy. This is a grouping of ICD-10-CM codes and SNOMED CT codes.),(Exclusion Criteria: Excludes concepts that pertain to the ectopic pregnancies other than cornual ectopic pregnancies, such as tubal ectopic pregnancies.)
